# python 配列
import numpy as np
x = np.arange(-10,10,1)
y = x**2 + 2.*x  + 10

print('x', x)
print('y', y)

y = np.cos(x)
plt.plot(x,y)
plt.show()

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

fig   =  plt.figure(figsize= (5,4))

plt.xlabel('longitude')
plt.ylabel('latitude')
